<P>
   It is time to end the monkey business over the banana war.
</P>
<P>
   The World Trade Organization (WTO) ruled on Tuesday that the
United States may impose $191 million worth of duties on goods from
the European Union (EU).
</P>
<P>
   While true that the behavior of the United States has certainly
been bullying, the Europeans now need to negotiate, not appeal.
</P>
<P>
   With more people fleeing from Kosovo and the number of deaths
increasing daily, the preoccupied western allies do not now need to
be wrangling over who is top banana. &QL;
