<HEADLINE>
ARIEL SHARON FEARS AN INDEPENDENT KOSOVO  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (TIMELY: Sharon meets with Madeleine Albright TODAY, FRIDAY)   (This TIMELY 525-word ``separate buy'' article is from The
Independent newspaper in London.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada EXCEPT to The Hamilton (Ontario) Spectator.)  
  
