moment. Ubiquitous on the airwaves during the Kosovo crisis, he is
trying to jumpstart his presidential bid. By Jill Zuckman. 1550
words.
</P>
<P>
   NY-MAGICIAN (New York) _ Magician's vow to spend six days in a
glass coffin has become quite the New York moment, drawing huge
crowds to witness perhaps the least dramatic magic trick _ a true
case of reverse Houdini _ in history. By Fred Kaplan. 725 words.
</P>
