<P>
   COXNET SCIHEALTH 0413 _ Some scientists who study the universe
without regard to the theories of creationists are beginning to ask
if Something did, after all, create everything _ not in six days of
cosmic spectacle a few thousand years ago but in the instantaneous
``big bang'' billions of years ago. (Nesmith, Cox Washington
Bureau)
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   DOGGIE DRINK _ What we're missing is Air Fidos, expensive
sneakers to allow your dog to reach its full athletic potential.
Instead, there's a new sports beverage _ for dogs. (Scott, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   HEALTH BRIEFS _ (Staff, Cox News Service)
</P>
<P>
   NEW-CONTACTLENS _ Ciba, the contact lens manufacturer based in
