   FBN-PATRIOTS-EDWARDS (Foxborough, Mass.) _ Robert Edwards was
really trying to be inconspicuous on his journey back to Foxboro.
Then Patriots owner Robert Kraft called him into his office and
handed him an envelope. By Nick Cafardo. 1100 words.
</P>
