   NATIONAL NEWS (``a'' category)
</P>
<P>
   RANCH-AUCTION (San Antonio) _ One of Texas' more opulent
ranches, Crawford Farms, is on the auction block again. The seller
this time is the Rev. Sun Myung Moon of the Unification Church, who
paid more than $8 million for the spread in 1992. By DAVID
HENDRICKS.
</P>
