<SLUG> BC-RUTTING-RAMS-EXHAUSTED(NEW-SCIENTIST)-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
WHEN TOO MUCH SEX IS EXHAUSTING  
 (FOR RELEASE THE WEEK OF MON., APRIL 12, 1999)
